448
00:29:30,376 --> 00:29:33,545
Adakah awak ada
ramai tetamu di hotel sekarang?

449
00:29:33,747 --> 00:29:35,378
Saya tidak nampak orang lain...

450
00:29:35,403 --> 00:29:37,417
selain dari pekerja hotel sekarang.

451
00:29:40,578 --> 00:29:41,888
Ada beberapa.

452
00:29:43,681 --> 00:29:45,641
Cik Jang ada di sana.

453
00:30:06,086 --> 00:30:08,446
