907
01:05:21,180 --> 01:05:22,973
Bukankah dia mati di Shanghai?

908
01:05:25,929 --> 01:05:28,863
Oh Tuhan, bau kopi ini sangat bagus.
Awak patut minum secawan lagi.

909
01:05:56,160 --> 01:05:57,574
